**Abstract:**
A list of library call numbers at the University of Dayton library for works consulted in the Chantilly project. References include works by Schofield and Nussbaum, MacIntyre, Aquinas, Barnes on Aristotle, Garrett Green on scriptural authority, Pegis on Aquinas, Nussbaum's Love's Knowledge and De Motu Animalium, Sokolowski's God of Faith and Reason, de Lubac on Christian faith, Chenu on faith and theology, Frei's Eclipse of Biblical Narrative, and Charlesworth on Anselm's Proslogion.

**AI Recommendation:** Practical research document listing library resources; useful for understanding the author's scholarly sources and research process.

